          <source>The following example uses a compound statement as the <bpt id="p1">*</bpt>statement<ept id="p1">*</ept> part of the <bpt id="p2">**</bpt>if<ept id="p2">**</ept> statement (see <bpt id="p3">[</bpt>The if Statement<ept id="p3">](../cpp/if-else-statement-cpp.md)</ept> for details about the syntax):</source>
